5f38696c   * and returns the OfflineAuditResult. session.ts calls this right after
b72d3b00   * tool registration to:
a7bbdfb3   *   - Print the [emmy] OFFLINE OK / NETWORK USED banner to stderr
03208703   *   - Feed the result into setInitialAudit + emitEvent("session.offline_audit.complete")
